---
title: Spicy Apricot Tofu with Garden Veggie Orzo
description: This meal truly has it all! Sweet, tangy and spicy tofu pieces are crisped before being cooked in a white wine-based sauce and served with veggie-packed orzo.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tofu-epice-aux-abricots-791582d5.jpg
